race.description: All Volunteer Bushfire Brigades Are Legends Maiden
race.comment: LATORIO (7) flew home at this track last time out, missing in a photo finish over 1407m. She's knocking on the door without winning and now getting out to the mile looks a big tick for her chances. Faithfull rides now and while she's drawn out, she can storm over the top to break her maiden. CLASSIC TURN (10) went 1800m back to 1407m last time out when behind LATORIO at this track. Back out to the mile looks a good move and she's got some solid ratings around this trip from earlier in this campaign. Drawn to settle a little closer today and can feature in the finish. TRULY SUPREME (8) missed over the 1400m at this track 20 days ago and steps out to this trip for the first time. It looks to suit with the way she finished off last start and she can make her presence felt. EXTRA ZERO (1) jumps right out in distance today and jumped an odds-on favourite under similar conditions when second-up last campaign. NOBLE TOUCH (11) is next best with the blinkers on first time.
